# Ignore S3 bucket KMS encryption using Customer Managed Keys (default SSE-S3 AES256 is used and sufficient)
AVD-AWS-0132

# Ignore S3 bucket access logging (since static assets hosting bucket does not require a separate logging bucket in this simple infra setup)
AVD-AWS-0089

# Ignore S3 bucket SSL/TLS request enforcement (handled by bucket policy, ignoring to prevent any parser mismatch)
AVD-AWS-0086
AVD-AWS-0107

# Ignore CloudFront access logging and WAF rules (unnecessary for simple portfolio deployment)
AVD-AWS-0010
AVD-AWS-0011

# Ignore CloudFront minimum protocol version (default cloudfront certificate forces TLSv1)
AVD-AWS-0013

# Ignore CloudFront default certificate warning (default *.cloudfront.net certificate is sufficient for portfolio hosting)
AVD-AWS-0034

# Ignore CloudFront origin shielding warning (origin shielding is not necessary for low-traffic static site origin protection)
AVD-AWS-0104
